==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Furthest
<hw>Fur"thest</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>superl. Most remote;
most in advance; farthest. See <er>Further</er>, <pos>a.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Furthest</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Furthest
<hw>Fur"thest</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>At the greatest distance;
farthest.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Furtive</ent>⟦br⟧
